{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-22-2",
 "title": "A Bored Colonel's Dogfight",
 "summary": "In the hangar bay of the NRSC Deliverance, Colonel Altair Quila lounges impatiently on her X-wing's wing while Bazil McKenzie cleans his blaster nearby, both waiting for cadets to finish chores so a mock dogfight can begin. Meanwhile, Representative Eva Sargent seeks out the prickly Sergeant Lianna Blackledge to diagnose a hydraulic problem that made her freighter, the Internuncio, tilt on landing. Once enough pilots assemble -- Altair, Bazil in Ghost 5, Wedge in Rogue One, Avitar in his A-wing, and the green cadet Vek Eldar in Ghost 11 -- they launch into space and split into teams for a practice battle. Altair opens by torpedoing the startled rookie before dueling Wedge, and the pilots trade rolls and laser fire until fresh fighters arrive to relieve the downed combatants and the session breaks off.",
